---
title: Beef Tenderloin Skewers with Charred Sweet Corn and Chipotle-Lime Butter
description: This isn’t your ordinary BBQ. Beef tenderloin is the creme de la creme of steak - so tender (when baked or grilled) you could practically cut it with a spoon. The smoky heat of chipotle mixed with the tang of lime and crunch of sweet corn will leave you begging for seconds.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-tenderloin-skewers-a943b6a8.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/beef-tenderloin-skewers-4c4e846b.pdf
cuisine: North America
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
nutrition:
  calories: 531 kcal
  fat: 27 g
  saturated fat: 11 g
  carbohydrates: 32 g
  sugar: 11 g
  protein: 43 g
  fiber: 7 g
  sodium: 121 mg
time required: 30 minutes
course: main course
